HAI 1.4
    I HAS A rows ITZ 5
    I HAS A i ITZ 0
    IM IN YR outer UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN rows
        I HAS A line ITZ ""
        I HAS A j ITZ 0
        IM IN YR inner UPPIN YR j TIL BOTH SAEM j AN SUM OF i AN 1
            line R SMOOSH line AN "* " MKAY
        IM OUTTA YR inner
        VISIBLE line
    IM OUTTA YR outer
KTHXBYE
